extendedInfo.description: Every darter needs to know the outs for x01 game.  Now it is quick and at your finger tips.No need to switch between pages to get the outs.  Updates on the page with quick access to the next out.The One app that every darter needs.Know your 3 dart and 2 dart outs.  Quickly get your outs without switching from one screen to another. Darts is an exciting game and knowing is half the battle.Be the one person on your team that has the answers.

reviews.title: great!!
reviews.comment: love that it instantly provides the out in case a single is hit. also it provides area to shoot at on some set ups. great!!

reviews.title: Wrong Out
reviews.comment: The dart out for 153 is wrong, it shows T20,-T18-D18. It should be T20-T19-D18. Mistakes are also noted for 84, It shows S20 leaves T16-D18.... It should be S20 leaves T16-D8. Otherwise, this is a good apps.
reviews.author: A Google User
